tuples.review: Sector 48 is a developed residential cum commercial locality situated along Sohna Road. The locality is conveniently placed near other developed sectors such as Sector 47, 49, 50 and therefore enjoys easy access to several schools, markets, hospitals and entertainment avenues nearby. Sector 48 hosts a good mix of builder floors, multi-storey apartments and villas, majorly catering to the upper-mid and premium segment. The sector has several educational institutions, healthcare facilities, restaurants, malls, shopping markets and banks, in and around its vicinity. Numerous shopping avenues in the area are Omaxe Celebration Mall, Raheja Mall, ILD Trade Centre, Omaxe City Centre and Omaxe Gurgaon Mall. Renowned schools and hospitals within a radius of 5 km are GD Goenka Public School, DAV Public School, St. Xavier's High School, Mount Olympus School, Presidium School, Park Hospital, Artemis Hospital and Medanta - The Medicity.Sector 48 has presence of several business centres in and around its vicinity. These include Bestech Business Park, IRIS Tech Park, JMD Megapolis, Unitech Infospace, Orchid Business Park and Candor Techspace. Various organisations operate from these office hubs such as Concentrix, Capgemini, Aon, Xceedance, Cognizant, etc. Moreover, Cyber City and Udyog Vihar commercial areas are easily accessible via NH-48 in about 30-35 minutes.
